SIGN-UP FOR A PLAY STREET ON 22 SEPTEMBER 2019
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Families in Richmond are again being invited to come out and play
    as part of a national Car Free Day this September, with a scheme
    aimed at encouraging children to play outside.

    Following last year's successful trial, Richmond Council is
    encouraging people to hold a play street on the 22nd September,
    by offering to close their roads to through-traffic for up to
    four hours.

